Hello everyone!

I know many of you are struggling with getting YAGSL up and running; and many more already have it up and running. To help these teams struggling I would love it if your team could post a link to their code or configuration with the description of the hardware in the following format

Module Type: Thrifty Swerve v2
Gyro: Pigeon2
Absolute Encoder: CANCoder
Angle Motor: NEOv1.1
Drive Motor: Krakenx40
Configs: https://github.com/BroncBotz3481/FRC2025/ (`comp` branch)
YAGSL Version: 2025.3.1-beta4

Last year i tried to maintain an example repository with configs but that didn’t gain any traction so i hope this will instead!

Good luck this year!
